WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:02.566
Xiao Du is asleep

2
00:00:02.666 --> 00:00:05.833
Before going to bed, he made me promise to be nice to my mother

3
00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:08.233
What a good boy

4
00:00:08.333 --> 00:00:09.766
I'll comb it for you.

5
00:00:14.466 --> 00:00:15.266
Ah!

6
00:00:15.766 --> 00:00:16.600
Don't be afraid.

7
00:00:17.666 --> 00:00:19.166
Why is there a power outage?

8
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:21.066
It must be on the wire

9
00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:23.700
Don't move.

10
00:00:24.366 --> 00:00:26.200
If you move around, you will fall.

11
00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:28.266
Come and let me help you

12
00:00:28.466 --> 00:00:29.966
Come on, get up.

13
00:00:32.466 --> 00:00:33.666
Good sit

14
00:00:40.700 --> 00:00:42.366
Can you let me go now?

15
00:00:42.466 --> 00:00:43.600
I lied to you.

16
00:00:44.266 --> 00:00:45.833
I will always hold you

17
00:00:46.166 --> 00:00:47.300
Keep hugging you

18
00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:48.400
Mount Zhuowei

19
00:00:49.066 --> 00:00:50.266
Just this once.

20
00:00:55.900 --> 00:00:58.133
Mom and Dad really made up

21
00:00:58.133 --> 00:00:59.500
Brother really has you

22
00:00:59.533 --> 00:01:01.333
The next time mom and dad quarrel

23
00:01:01.333 --> 00:01:02.500
I also use this trick

24
00:01:02.733 --> 00:01:04.100
It's better in winter.

25
00:01:04.100 --> 00:01:06.066
A basin of water goes down and you catch a cold

26
00:01:06.066 --> 00:01:07.466
Do you want me to help you with the water?

27
00:01:07.566 --> 00:01:08.633
Save the trouble

28
00:01:09.133 --> 00:01:11.100
Dad, I'm talking nonsense.

29
00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:13.166
Come and let's have a good chat with father and son

